oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: George Thomas and Carl Dieckman perform Anniversary Blue Yodel and T.B. Blues
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: George Thomas and Carl Dieckman perform Anniversary Blue Yodel and T.B. Blues around the time of the 1953 Jimmie Rodgers Memorial Day. An image of the possible location of the recording can be seen here: http://dc.lib.unc.edu/cdm/singleitem/collection/sfc/id/26637/rec/2 . Content similar to [ TR001740_1 ].
